## 6. Tables Involved

### 6.1 Sales Group

Existing parent table representing the commercial grouping.

Key required field used by this solution:

* Sales Group primary name field (existing)

### 6.2 Account

Standard Account table.

Required field used by this solution:

* `prm_salesgroupid` (Lookup to Sales Group)

### 6.3 Promotion Header

New custom table to store campaign-level promotion data.

### 6.4 Promotion Line

New custom table to store line/product-level data beneath each Promotion Header.

